</span></dd></dl>
<p>If <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>A</b></span> is an <span class=3D"texhtml"=
><span class=3D"nowrap"><i>m</i> =C3=97 <i>n</i></span></span> matrix, then=
 <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>A</b><sup>T</sup></span> is an <span class=3D"t=
exhtml"><span class=3D"nowrap"><i>n</i> =C3=97 <i>m</i></span></span> matri=
x.=20
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Matrix_definitions_involvin=
g_transposition">Matrix definitions involving transposition</h4><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=
