      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \mathbf {A} ^=
{\text{T}}=3D-\mathbf {A} .}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/931d7baf99b63acafc142273a288107f2f6ad7aa" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.505ex; width:11.011ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \m=
athbf {A} ^{\text{T}}=3D-\mathbf {A} .}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>A square <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_number" title=
=3D"Complex number">complex</a> matrix whose transpose is equal to the matr=
ix with every entry replaced by its <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Complex_conjugate" title=3D"Complex conjugate">complex conjugate</a> (den=
oted here with an overline) is called a <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/wiki/Hermitian_matrix" title=3D"Hermitian matrix">Hermitian matrix</a><=
/i> (equivalent to the matrix being equal to its <a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/wiki/Conjugate_transpose" title=3D"Conjugate transpose">conjugate=
 transpose</a>); that is, <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>A</b></span> is Hermit=
ian if
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
